  'Choice B is the best answer. The text describes Favela''s approach to sculpture, and then describes the lowrider car that he depicted in 2017. Choice A is incorrect. This isn''t what the text says. The Petersen Automotive Museum is located in Los Angeles, but Favela''s artwork isn''t a painting, and it doesn''t depict L.A. Choice C is incorrect. This isn''t what the text says. Favela makes sculptures similar to piñatas, not paintings of them. Choice D is incorrect. This isn''t what the text says. Jesse Valadez owned the lowrider car that Favela depicted in sculpture.',
